tests.name: Pre-test Setup
tests.setup: git clone https://github.com/mikeryu/westmont-cs128-f23-a01-textprocessing-instout.git && cd ./src && pwd && md5sum ./run_all.sh | grep "5edb8ec835a4e801a649f74540c5e6a3" && chmod 777 ./run_all.sh && echo "Setup complete."
tests.run: cd ./src && pwd && ls -la && ./run_all.sh &> ../out/run_all.out.txt && cat ../out/run_all.out.txt && echo "Completed running run_all.sh"
